phrases: The day I moved to Enoshima,
I met the self-proclaimed alien, Haru.
I do not have any interest in fishing,
but he forced me into it with his mysterious water gun.
The fishing prince, Natsuki, was super harsh...
and for some reason, I am living with that alien.
Haru, you should not make so much noise when you eat.
I did not realize aliens also ate miso soup
Why is he eating like he belongs here?
I am glad you are here, Haru.
Grandma does some unbelievable things sometimes.
She will not listen to anything I say
Yuki, it is a scary cat!
You are way scarier than the cat.
Is that the duo I have heard about?
They are real weird, are not they?
Maybe they will put on a show for us.
Please do not associate me with this weirdo.
I just wanted to have a normal school life this time,
but now everyone thinks I am a weirdo!
I cannot take it any more!
Thank you for looking after my brother.
I am sure my brother has already told you,
but there is a fish we have got to catch...
I do not care what it was.
If you do not catch it soon, we cannot return to our planet.
If you will not help us, you will be in big trouble.
You are the only one who can save it.
You got to be kidding me!
Why do I have to save Earth?
Then go catch one for the day.
If you break it, the next time
we meet will be on top of the Sky Tree.
I want to go to the Sky Tree!
I definitely thought you would quit.
I could not quit even if I wanted to.
Hey, teach us to fish, Prince.
Say that again, and I will kill you.
You really should listen to him.
Cannot this guy follow a conversation?
And why is not he talking?
Between this and breaking out into the Enoshima dance,
Why do not you go for some sea bass?
In the Japanese lure fishing community,
suzuki is known as sea bass.
I want to catch sea bass.
my brother hanging out with his friends.
He is a completely different guy in front of his sister.
Sakura-chan, Natsuki's going to teach us how to fish.
My brother's really good at fishing.
I am sure you will catch something.
Even if you fall in, you will float if you are wearing that.
You wear it when you go sea fishing.
Fishing starts with assembling your tackle.
We are supposed to put together all of this?
Sounds like a lot of work.
I just have to catch one, right?
Listen up, because I will only say it once.
First attach your reel to your rod, and open the bail arm.
Pull out your line, and thread it through the guides.
Then, attach the lure to the leader on the end of your line.
You can borrow one of my lures.
What the heck is he doing?!
Tie this with a uni knot.
It is a way to tie your line.
I am only going to show you once.
Pass the line through the hole in this metal snap.
Make a ring, and go around three times.
If you do not tie it right, it will come undone right away.
I said I would only show you once.
Yuki, make sure you remember this time.
Is this how he is been controlling me, too?
What am I going to do if I cannot catch a fish?
I am surprised you are such a fast learner.
He did not get it at all.
And why is he so mad?
Hey, do you need me to explain it again?
What am I going to do if I cannot catch a fish?
Do you want me to explain it to you again?
Yuki, why cannot you catch anything?
Besides, there is no way an amateur could suddenly catch
Um, what am I supposed to do again?
Raise your rod and calmly reel him in!
What am I going to do?
What am I going to do?!
Did you tie your uni knot right?
I am asking if you tied your knot right.
Who do you think's going to suffer if you do that?
Fishing's not something you can just wing.
I refuse to fish with someone who does that.
What should I say at a time like this?
I bet you did not even listen to anything I said!
Think about others a little more!
I am teaching you because you asked me to teach you!
Guys like you cannot do anything.
If you have something to say, say it!
He will never catch anything fishing like that.
I want to eat your curry now.
Did you have some of this?
It is a cheese roe whitebait ball.
What do you think you are doing?
It has not even been two years.
What are you getting embarrassed about?
You will feel a lot better with short hair.
I did not ask for your opinion.
There is no need to get so angry.
Yuki said he does not want to be my friend.
Does being with Yuki make you happy?
When your heart feels like this.
Then you should not bother him.
When Yuki wants to be alone, you should leave him alone.
When he wants to be alone, he is thinking about something.
About something important, I am sure.
If I leave him alone, will Yuki be my friend?
Do not do it in front of Yuki.
Who do you think's going to suffer if you do that?
Guys like you cannot do anything.
If you have something to say, say it!
You do not have to go that far!
I might have been winging it.
Hey Nii-chan, why do you like that Yuki kid?
I do not know, but I like him.
He is always making that weird face,
I do not think you should fish with him.
If I do that, we will be friends.
If we are friends, I know we can catch it.
It will not be that easy.
What am I supposed to do, then?
This will reduce the friction and keep it from breaking.
But I need to be able to tie it faster.
I just do not like it.
I will catch something this time.
I will not wing it any more.
There is no reason you cannot do at least that.
I want you to teach me to fish.
I am transferring into this class today.
but do not let that stop us from being friends.
It is a pleasure to meet you.
The four of us came together for the first time that day.
